series.renderItem: function (params, api) { var x = api.value(0), y = api.value(1), dx = api.value(2), dy = api.value(3); var start = api.coord([x - dx / 2, y - dy / 2]); var end = api.coord([x + dx / 2, y + dy / 2]); return { type: 'line', shape: { x1: start[0], y1: start[1], x2: end[0], y2: end[1] }, style: { lineWidth: 2, stroke: '#fff', opacity: 0.2 } }; }
